gov.va.vinci.leo.descriptors

Annotation Type LeoConfigurationParameter


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
 @Inherited
public @interface LeoConfigurationParameter
    Marks a class field variable as a configuration parameter. Supported types include primitives, Strings, and objects with a single string parameter in the constructor. Parameter types are set from the field type. Field array variables are created as multi-valued parameters. User: Thomas Ginter Date: 10/22/14 Time: 16:14
